msgctxt "203059	MORE_EXPLANATION1"
msgid "Kiryu\n"
"\n"
"I heard you had returned to Kamurocho and\n"
" set to penning this letter at once. \n"
"Currently, I am in charge of a dojo\n"
" at the Dragon Palace, but I \n"
"recently had to leave the dojo unsupervised\n"
" for a small trip. I \n"
"understand that during my absence,\n"
" you fought off a few unruly \n"
"troublemakers that appeared there. \n"
"Words cannot express my gratitude."
msgstr "Kiryu\n"
"\n"
"Escuché que habías regresado a Kamurocho y\n"
" empeze a escribir esta carta sin falta. \n"
"Actualmente, estoy a cargo de un dojo\n"
" en el Palacio del Dragón, pero yo \n"
"Recientemente tuve que dejar el dojo sin supervisión\n"
" para un viaje pequeño. Yo \n"
"comprenda que durante mi ausencia,\n"
" Luchaste contra algunos rebeldes \n"
"alborotadores que aparecieron allí. \n"
"No hay palabras para expresar mi gratitud."

msgctxt "203416	MORE_EXPLANATION1"
msgid "Heaven...Dragon King\n"
"Earth...Bowl\n"
"Man...Swordless"
msgstr "Cielo... Rey Dragón\n"
"Tierra... Tazón\n"
"Hombre... Swordless"

msgctxt "203469	MORE_EXPLANATION1"
msgid "Fishing Tips-\n"
"\n"
"The trick to good fishing is to keep that\n"
"line from snapping. If the tension's too\n"
"tight, it'll break, but if it's too loose,\n"
"the fish'll get away. If you think it's\n"
"getting too tight, lower the pole in sync\n"
"with the movement of the fish. If that\n"
"doesn't work, then loosen up the line."
msgstr "Consejos de pesca-\n"
"\n"
"El truco para una buena pesca es mantener eso\n"
"línea de ajuste. Si la tensión es demasiado\n"
"apretada, se romperá, pero si está demasiado suelto, los peces se escaparán. Si crees que es\n"
"apretando demasiado, baja la caña en sincronía\n"
"con el movimiento de los peces. Si eso\n"
"no funciona, entonces afloje el hilo."

