msgctxt "208811	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "It seems the peaceful \n"
"life has not dulled your keen edge.\n"
" Knowing you, however, I suspect your \n"
"peaceful life may soon be \n"
"at its end. If you ever feel \n"
"the need to train once more, \n"
"please stop by the Dragon Palace. \n"
"I would be more than happy to \n"
"whip you into shape once more.\n"
" It would be good if you did; \n"
"there is one thing I may require your \n"
"assistance with, but I would rather \n"
"speak of it in person. \n"
"Signed Sotaro Komaki, Komaki Dojo."
msgstr "Por lo que he oído, la vida tranquila no te ha hecho\n"
"perder tu forma. Pero conociéndote, sospecho\n"
"que tu vida pacífica no durará mucho.\n"
"Si alguna vez sientes la necesidad de entrenar de nuevo,\n"
"por favor ven al Palacio del Dragón. Estaré encantado de\n"
"ponerte en forma. Solo escríbeme.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, hay cierta cosa en la cual necesito\n"
"tu ayuda. Te diré más cuando nos encontremos\n"
"en persona.\n"
"\n"
"Firmado Sotaro Komaki, Komaki Dojo."

msgctxt "209262	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "Fishing Tips-\n"
"\n"
"Stronger fish tend to quickly increase line\n"
"tension. When this happens, try pulling the pole\n"
"up, then lowering it while reeling in the line.\n"
"When doing this repeatedly, you should even be\n"
"able to pull in the big one!"
msgstr "Consejos de pesca-\n"
"\n"
"Los peces más fuertes tienden a aumentar rápidamente la línea\n"
"tensión. Cuando esto suceda, intente tirar del poste\n"
"hacia arriba, luego bajándolo mientras se enrolla en la línea.\n"
"Al hacer esto repetidamente, ya deberias ser\n"
"¡Capaz de pescar a los mas grandes!"

msgctxt "209496	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "You've completed Legend mode.\n"
"Congratulations! You are worthy of the\n"
"title Heir to the Legend."
msgstr "Has completado el modo Leyenda.\n"
"¡Felicidades! Eres digno de la\n"
"título Heredero de la Leyenda."

msgctxt "209593	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "You've completed all of the Ultimate\n"
"Skill missions. Congratulations! You are\n"
"worthy of the title Ultimate Man."
msgstr "Has completado todo el Ultimate\n"
"Misiones de habilidad. ¡Felicidades! Tú\n"
"digno del título de Hombre Ultimate."

msgctxt "209707	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "You've completed all of Saejima's\n"
"substories. Congratulations! You are\n"
"worthy of the title Saejimaniac."
msgstr "Has completado todos los errores de Saejima.\n"
"historias secundarias. ¡Felicidades! Tú\n"
"digno del título de Saejimaniaco."

msgctxt "209813	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
msgid "You've defeated Amon handily.\n"
"Congratulations! You are worthy of the\n"
"title Men of Legend."
msgstr "Has derrotado a Amon fácilmente.\n"
"¡Felicidades! Eres digno de la\n"
"título Hombres de Leyenda."

msgctxt "209905	MORE_EXPLANATION2"
