msgctxt "215654	MORE_EXPLANATION4"
msgid "Cardio Enhancing Running Shirt-\n"
"\n"
"Physimagic Jersey as a base plus:\n"
"1. Toughness Z\n"
"2. Staminan X\n"
"\n"
"-High-Tech Shin Guards-\n"
"\n"
"Plastic Shin Guards as a base plus:\n"
"1. Durable Cloth\n"
"2. Synthetic Polymer"
msgstr "Camiseta de running que mejora el cardio-\n"
"\n"
"Maillot Physimagic como base más:\n"
"1. Dureza Z\n"
"2. Staminan X\n"
"\n"
"-Espinilleras de alta tecnología-\n"
"\n"
"Espinilleras de plástico como base más:\n"
"1. Tela duradera\n"
"2. Polímero sintético"

msgctxt "215853	MORE_EXPLANATION4"
msgid "Fishing Tips-\n"
"\n"
"Every now and then you can pull up a\n"
"beautiful, top-grade fish. You'll work\n"
"up a mean sweat, but there's nothing like\n"
"the satisfaction of landing that sucker!\n"
"Give it a shot!"
msgstr "Consejos de pesca-\n"
"\n"
"En algún momento podrás pescar un precioso pez de alta calidad.\n"
"Tendrás que sudar cada gota para conseguirlo, ¡Pero no hay nada más \n"
"satisfactorio que atrapar a esos desgraciados!\n"
"¡Inténtalo!"

